Summary: Dino Rush is a free endless runner game. We do not personally identify you, sell your data, or require account registration. Ads are served by Google AdMob.

1. Information We Collect
Dino Rush does not collect, store, or transmit any personally identifiable information. Game preferences and high scores are stored locally on your device only.

Non-personal data that may be collected by third-party services:

Device type, model, and operating system version
Advertising ID (for serving relevant ads)
General location (country/region level only)
App interaction and crash logs
2. How We Use Information
Data is used solely to display advertisements, analyze app performance, and comply with applicable laws. We do not sell, trade, or share any user data with third parties.

3. Google AdMob
This app uses Google AdMob to display advertisements. AdMob may collect and process data per Google's Privacy Policy:

https://policies.google.com/privacy
https://support.google.com/admob/answer/6128543
To opt out of personalized ads: Settings → Google → Ads → Opt out of Ads Personalization.

4. Permissions Used

INTERNET – Required to load advertisements
ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE – Check connectivity before loading ads
VIBRATE – Haptic feedback during gameplay
5. Children's Privacy
Dino Rush is intended for a general audience. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13.

6. Data Retention
All game data is stored locally on your device and deleted when you uninstall the app. We retain no data on external servers.

7. Changes to This Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be reflected on this page with a revised date.

